title: Eating Only Onions for 24 Hours: How Many Onions Does it Take to Kill a Man?
description: As Shrek once told me in a dark alley on a stormy night, 'Onions have layers'... That message has been cemented into my mind among other things Shrek whispered into my ear. But in this video we discover the true versatility of the mythical Onion and if there is such a thing as too much Onion.
